    "en": {
      "title": "18 cabinet ministers take oath",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Cabinet of Ministers took oath in front of President Ranil Wickramasinghe.",
        "The oath was administered at the Prime Minister's Secretariat at Mal Road, Colombo.",
        "Dinesh Gunawardena, Douglas Devananda, Susil Prema Jayantha, Bandula Gunawardena, Keheliya Rambukwella, Mahinda Amaraweera, Wijedasa Rajapaksa, Harin Fernando, Ramesh Pathirana, Prasanna Ranatunga, Ali Sabri, Vidura Wickramanayake, Kanchana Wijesekera, Naseer Ahmed, Roshan Ranasinghe, Manusha Nanayakkara, Tiran Messrs. Alas and Nalin Fernando took the oath."
      ],
